              "keyParts": [
                24,
                "p1",
                "verse",
                "v5",
                "content"
              ],
              "value": "But if she bears a female child, then she shall be unclean two weeks, as in her menstruation. And she shall continue in the blood of her purifying for sixty-six days."
            },
            {
              "rowId": 25,
              "keyParts": [
                "v005_ESV_LEV_012",
                25,
                "p1",
                "verse",
                "v5",
                "plain_text"
              ],
              "value": "5 But if she bears a female child, then she shall be unclean two weeks, as in her menstruation. And she shall continue in the blood of her purifying for sixty-six days."
